# --- Terraform State (Recursively) ---
**/.terraform/
*.tfstate*
.terraform.lock.hcl

# --- Generated Config (Recursively) ---
# The **/ prefix tells Git to look in every subfolder
**/backend.hcl
**/backend.ci.hcl
**/*.tfvars

# --- Tooling & Binaries ---
terraform-docs
tflint
trivy
aws/
awscliv2.zip
.cache/

# Ignore the local install of the layer libraries
infra/modules/vstshop/backend/layer/python/
# Ignore the generated zips
infra/modules/vstshop/backend/*.zip

# --- Python Bytecode ---
# Prevents __pycache__ folders from cluttering your Lambda modules
**/__pycache__/
**/*.py[cod]
**/*$py.class

# --- Environment Secrets ---
# Sometimes developers create .env files inside module folders
**/.env
**/.env.*

# --- Terraform Crash Logs ---
# If Terraform crashes, it writes a huge trace file
crash.log
**/terraform.debug

# --- OS Specific Junk ---
# Especially important if you collaborate with Mac/Windows users
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
